FBIS3-8597 "dreeu049_a_94004" FBIS-EEU-94-049 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Mar 1994 ALBANIA Swiss Branch of PDP To Meet Unpaid Debt AU1303205694 Tirana TVSH Television Network in Albanian 1900 GMT 13 Mar 94 AU1303205694 Tirana TVSH Television Network Language: Albanian Article Type:BFN [Text] The Presidency of the Party for Democratic Prosperity [PDP] branch in Switzerland reports that in a meeting in Zurich on 12 March, the presidency decided that this party branch will meet a part of the unpaid obligation of the Albanian population in the former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia concerning the investments for the satellite program project. This branch will ensure a sum of 300,000 Swiss francs until 1 May 1994. The money will be deposited in the account of the satellite program of the Albanian Radio-Television.
